The chairman of the National Drug Law Enforcement Agency, Buba Marwa over the weekend buried his late wife, Mrs Salome Zainab Marwa in Emekuku, Owerri North Local Government Area of Imo State.



Late Mrs Marwa was the sister of the former governorship candidate in Imo State, Martin Agbaso and Jude Agbaso, a former Deputy Governor of the state.



Some of the dignitaries at the burial include Peter Obi, Anambra PDP governorship candidate, Valentine Ozigbo, among others.

